HEADWORD: Leathery
<hw>Leath"er*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Resembling leather
in appearance or consistency; tough; <as>as, nothing but a
<ex>leathery</ex> steak left to eat</as>.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A
<xex>leathery</xex> skin.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Grew.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
